<i>noun</i>: 소독 [소독], 살균 [살균], 멸균 [멸균] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>소독 [소독]</dt><br>
<dd>disinfection; sterilization</dd><br>
<dd>병에 걸리는 것을 막기 위해 약품이나 열 등으로 균을 죽임.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of destroying germs with chemicals, heat, etc., in order to prevent one's getting sick.</dd><br>
<dt>살균 [살균]</dt><br>
<dd>sterilization</dd><br>
<dd>약품이나 열 등을 이용해 세균을 죽여 없앰.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of killing germs through chemicals, heat, etc.</dd><br>
<dt>멸균 [멸균]</dt><br>
<dd>sterilization</dd><br>
<dd>약품이나 열 등을 이용하여 세균을 죽여 없앰.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of killing microorganisms through the use of chemicals or heat.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>